      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with it\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh new car smell. I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
