    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 powerhouse, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, with the rear subframe meticulously inspected and verified. Finished in its original factory glaze, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, reflecting a lifetime of climate-controlled storage. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. No deferred maintenance; every bushing, seal, and fluid is current. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist who demands mechanical perfection and historical authenticity.",
